channel.title: Need Help With Opening Port/Port Foward [problem resolved]
channel.description:
Hello guys, I previously tried to portforward an Rsps Port of 43594 to try to beta test it with my friends, but when i go and check to see if the port was open on www.canyouseeme.org it said that there is a Connection TimeOut Error. I have tried many ways to fix it, but it never seems to work so i was hoping one you fellows might be able help me resolve this problem.
Skype: Melilshaw3

item.title: Need Help With Opening Port/Port Foward [problem resolved]
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

[quote=“Pure Shaw, post:3, topic:552458”][quote author=sk8rdude461 link=topic=671377.msg4489878#msg4489878 date=1436968499]
When you went to test, did you make sure the server was online when you did?
[/quote]
No i didnt[/quote]
Try it again with the server online. Make sure the server has finished loading fully before testing.

Read full topic
